0&amp;q=80\" alt=\"About batyspestcontrol\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover opacity-30\"/><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-900 via-brand-900/90 to-brand-900/70\"></div></div><div class=\"container mx-auto px-4 max-w-7xl relative z-10\"><div class=\"max-w-3xl\"><nav class=\"text-sm mb-6\" aria-label=\"Breadcrumb\"><ol class=\"flex items-center space-x-2\"><li><a class=\"text-surface-400 hover:text-accent-500 transition\" href=\"/\">Home</a></li><li><span class=\"text-surface-600 mx-2\">/</span></li><li><span class=\"text-accent-500 font-medium\">About Us</span></li></ol></nav><span class=\"inline-block bg-accent-500 text-brand-900 font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest px-4 py-2 rounded mb-6 shadow-md\">Pest Control Experts</span><h1 class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-black mb-6 text-white leading-tight\">About batyspestcontrol</h1><p class=\"text-xl text-surface-300 mb-8 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed\">Your trusted pest control professionals serving homeowners and businesses nationwide with fast, effective, and eco-friendly extermination services.</p><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-4\"><a href=\"tel:614-926-0787\" class=\"inline-flex items-center bg-accent-500 text-brand-900 px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg hover:bg-accent-600 transition shadow-xl\"><span class=\"mr-3 text-xl\">📞</span>614-926-0787</a><a class=\"inline-flex items-center bg-white text-brand-900 px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg hover:bg-surface-100 transition shadow-lg\" href=\"/contact\"><span class=\"mr-3 text-xl\">✉️</span>Contact Us</a></div></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-accent-500 py-10\"><div class=\"container mx-auto px-4 max-w-7xl\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 text-center divide-x divide-brand-900/10\"><div><div class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-brand-900 mb-2\">15+</div><div class=\"text-brand-900/80 font-bold tracking-wide uppercase text-sm\">Services</div></div><div><div class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-brand-900 mb-2\">50+</div><div class=\"text-brand-900/80 font-bold tracking-wide uppercase text-sm\">Cities Served</div></div><div><div class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-brand-900 mb-2\">5★</div><div class=\"text-brand-900/80 font-bold tracking-wide uppercase text-sm\">Rating</div></div><div><div class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-brand-900 mb-2\">24/7</div><div class=\"text-brand-900/80 font-bold tracking-wide uppercase text-sm\">Available</div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-16 md:py-24 bg-surface-50\"><div class=\"container mx-auto px-4 max-w-7xl\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-start\"><div class=\"lg:col-span-5\"><div class=\"sticky top-24\"><div class=\"relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl\"><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1540555700478-4be289fbecef?auto=format&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=800&amp;q=80\" alt=\"Pest Control Professionals\" class=\"w-full aspect-[4/3] object-cover\" loading=\"lazy\"/><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-brand-900/80 via-transparent to-transparent\"></div><div class=\"absolute bottom-4 left-4 right-4\"><div class=\"bg-white/95 backdrop-blur-md rounded-xl p-4 shadow-lg border border-white/20\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><div class=\"flex items-center\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-accent-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-3 shadow-inner\"><span class=\"text-brand-900 text-xl\">🏆</span></div><div><p class=\"font-extrabold text-brand-900\">100% Satisfaction</p><p class=\"text-xs text-surface-500 font-medium tracking-wide uppercase\">Licensed &amp; Insured</p></div></div><div class=\"text-right\"><div class=\"flex text-accent-500 text-lg mb-1\">★★★★★</div><p class=\"text-[10px] text-surface-500 font-bold uppercase tracking-wider\">5-Star Rated</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 mt-6\"><div class=\"bg-white rounded-xl p-5 text-center border border-surface-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition\"><div class=\"text-3xl mb-3 text-emerald-500\">🛡️</div><p class=\"font-bold text-brand-900 text-sm\">Licensed</p></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-xl p-5 text-center border border-surface-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition\"><div class=\"text-3xl mb-3 text-blue-500\">📄</div><p class=\"font-bold text-brand-900 text-sm\">Insured</p></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-xl p-5 text-center border border-surface-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition\"><div class=\"text-3xl mb-3 text-accent-500\">⚡</div><p class=\"font-bold text-brand-900 text-sm\">Fast Response</p></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-xl p-5 text-center border border-surface-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition\"><div class=\"text-3xl mb-3 text-purple-500\">💲</div><p class=\"font-bold text-brand-900 text-sm\">Fair Pricing</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"lg:col-span-7\"><span class=\"inline-block bg-accent-500/10 text-brand-600 font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest px-4 py-2 rounded-full mb-6\">Who We Are</span><h2 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-black text-brand-900 mb-8 leading-tight\">Your Nationwide Pest Control Professionals</h2><div class=\"prose prose-lg max-w-none text-surface-600 prose-headings:text-brand-900 prose-headings:font-bold prose-a:text-accent-600 mb-10\"><p class=\"text-xl leading-relaxed mb-6 font-medium text-surface-700\">With a network of highly trained and certified exterminators across the country, batyspestcontrol provides top-tier residential and commercial pest management solutions.</p><p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed\">We understand the unique challenges that different climates and regions present. Whether you are dealing with aggressive termite colonies in the South, seasonal rodent migrations in the North, or year-round ant invasions, our specialized teams have the local expertise and advanced treatments needed to eradicate the problem at its source.</p><h3 class=\"text-2xl mt-8 mb-4\">Our Core Capabilities</h3><ul class=\"space-y-3 mb-8\"><li class=\"flex items-start\"><span class=\"text-accent-500 mr-3 mt-1\">✔</span><span><strong>24/7 Emergency Services:</strong> Rapid response for severe infestations and hazardous pests like wasps or hornets.</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start\"><span class=\"text-accent-500 mr-3 mt-1\">✔</span><span><strong>Eco-Friendly Options:</strong> Safe, sustainable treatments that protect your family and pets while eliminating pests.</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start\"><span class=\"text-accent-500 mr-3 mt-1\">✔</span><span><strong>Comprehensive Inspections:</strong> Detailed property evaluations to identify entry points, nesting sites, and structural vulnerabilities.</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start\"><span class=\"text-accent-500 mr-3 mt-1\">✔</span><span><strong>Preventative Maintenance:</strong> Ongoing protection plans designed to keep your property pest-free year-round.</span></li></ul><p class=\"leading-relaxed\">Every service call includes a thorough inspection and a customized treatment plan. We don&#x27;t just spray and leave; we partner with you to implement long-term exclusion strategies. Our licensed professionals ensure all work is fully documented and complies with local and state regulations.</p></div><div class=\"bg-brand-900 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-10 text-white mt-12 relative overflow-hidden shadow-2xl\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 opacity-10\" style=\"background-image:url(&#x27;https://www.transparenttextures.com/patterns/carbon-fibre.png&#x27;)\"></div><div class=\"relative z-10 flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between gap-8\"><div><h3 class=\"text-2xl text-white font-bold mb-3 flex items-center\"><span class=\"text-accent-500 mr-3 text-3xl\">💬</span>Ready to Get Started?</h3><p class=\"text-surface-300 text-lg\">Contact us today for a free estimate on your pest control needs.</p></div><div class=\"flex shrink-0\"><a href=\"tel:614-926-0787\" class=\"inline-flex items-center bg-accent-500 text-brand-900 px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg hover:bg-accent-600 transition shadow-lg w-full md:w-auto justify-center\"><span class=\"mr-3 text-xl\">📞</span>614-926-0787</a></div></div></div></div></div></div></section></main><footer class=\"bg-[#0a1128] text-white pt-24 pb-20 md:pb-12 border-t border-brand-800 relative overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 opacity-5\" style=\"background-image:url(&#x27;https://www.transparenttextures.com/patterns/carbon-fibre.png&#x27;)\"></div><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 relative z-10 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-16 lg:gap-8\"><div class=\"space-y-6\"><a class=\"flex items-center gap-3\" href=\"/\"><div class=\"relative flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 bg-brand-900 rounded-xl shadow-lg border border-white/10\"><span class=\"text-2xl\">🛡️</span></div><div class=\"flex flex-col justify-center\"><span class=\"font-extrabold text-2xl tracking-tight leading-none text-white\">batyspestcontrol</span><span class=\"font-bold text-xs tracking-[0.2em] text-accent-500 uppercase mt-0.5\">Pest Control</span></div></a><p class=\"text-surface-400 text-sm leading-relaxed pr-4\">We provide fast, reliable, and eco-friendly pest control services nationwide. Available 24/7 for all your residential and commercial needs.</p><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 text-surface-400 text-sm\"><span class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"text-accent-500\">✓</span> Licensed</span><span class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"text-accent-500\">✓</span> Insured</span><span class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"text-accent-500\">✓</span> Bonded</span></div></div><div><h4 class=\"text-white font-bold mb-8 text-lg\">Our Services</h4><ul class=\"space-y-4 text-sm text-surface-400\"><li><a class=\"hover:text-accent-400 hover:translate-x-1 transition-all flex items-center gap-3\" href=\"/termite-treatment\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 text-[10px]\">■<